snippet.title: Army of Two The Devil's Cartel Trailer (Gamescom 2012)
snippet.description:
Army of Two The Devil's Cartel Trailer (Gamescom 2012). Join us on Facebook : http://facebook.com/GameNewsOfficial ! Tactical co-op is back as Alpha and Bravo, two operatives working for Tactical Worldwide Operations (T.W.O.) on the deadly streets of Mexico.

Army of Two The Devil Cartel Trailer (Gamescom 2012). Release date : March 2012 on PS3 and Xbox 360. Suscribe now to get all gameplay trailers and videos !
